With this motion made by Dr. Johnson and seconded by Ms. O'Herron, and after hearing the other opinions from the Board Members,  Motion carried with five yeses and two abstentions. This was provided electronically today to each of the board members via email. It contains lists of those who were employed, dismissed, or reassigned within our system since the last meeting. Moved by Ms. Le. A second? Seconded by Ms. Acuff. I've reviewed the material online. There were seven resignations and three new hires in that category, five transfers, 12 people hired.
